Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20extremely%20excited%20that%2C%20uh%2C%20today%2C%20Gaganyaan%20is%20getting%20ready%20and%20we%20are%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20really%20creating%20another%20historical%20moment.%20I%20believe%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20meaningful%20because%20here%20we%20are%20going%20to%20be%20launching%20an%20Indian%20launcher%20with%20the%20Indians%20on%20board%20from%20an%20Indian%20spaceport%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20praised%20the%20mission%20for%20being%20entirely%20indigenous%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20which%20is%20really%20worth%20looking%20forward%20to%20and%20worth%20celebrating%20because%20I'm%20extremely%20confident%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20very%20successful%20flight%2C%20God%20willing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExactly%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20on%20April%203%2C%201984%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20scripted%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20to%20reach%20outer%20space%20on%20board%20the%20Soviet%20rocket%20Soyuz%20T-11.%20When%20asked%20by%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20how%20India%20looked%20from%20space%2C%20he%20replied%20quoting%20poet%20Iqbal%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3ESaare%20jahaan%20se%20achcha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(better%20than%20the%20whole%20world)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20feels%20the%20same%2040%20years%20down%20the%20line%2C%20he%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20indeed%2C%20indeed.%20Of%20course%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712042880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3blng0h8_rakesh-sharma_625x300_02_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fastronaut-rakesh-sharma-on-why-gaganyaan-is-a-lot-more-meaningful-5357482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wing%20Commander%20Rakesh%20Sharma%2C%20the%20only%20Indian%20to%20have%20gone%20into%20the%20space%2C%20is%20excited%20to%20welcome%20more%20Indian%20astronau