20authorities%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JV%20will%20deliver%20automotive%20software%2C%20including%20Software-defined%20Vehicle%20(SDV)%20solutions%20for%20BMW%20Group's%20premium%20vehicles%20and%20digital%20transformation%20solutions%20for%20its%20business%20IT.%20It%20will%20commence%20operations%20with%20100%20innovators%20and%20%26quot%3Bintends%20to%20grow%20quickly%20to%20a%20four-digit%20number%20in%20the%20following%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JV%20will%20become%20part%20of%20BMW%20Group's%20global%20network%20of%20software%20and%20IT%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20collaboration%20with%20the%20BMW%20Group%20demonstrates%20our%20commitment%20to%20providing%20top-tier%20solutions%20in%20automotive%20software%20and%20digital%20engineering%20to%20customers%20across%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Tata%20Technologies%20CEO%20and%20MD%20Warren%20Harris%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20will%20aid%20BMW%20Group%20in%20engineering%20premium%20products%2C%20delivering%26quot%3B%20great%20digital%20experiences%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20customers%2C%20and%20propelling%20its%20digital%20transformation%20journey%20in%20business%20IT%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBMW%20Group%20Senior%20Vice%20President%20of%20Software%20and%20E%2FE%20Architecture%20Christoph%20Grote%20said%20the%20collaboration%20with%20Tata%20Technologies%20will%20accelerate%20BMW's%20progress%20in%20the%20field%20of%20the%20software-defined%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20international%20comparison%2C%20India%20boasts%20a%20large%20number%20of%20talents%20with%20outstanding%20software%20skills%2C%20who%20can%20contribute%20to%20our%20software%20competence%2C%26quot%3B%20Grote%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20said%20developing%20vehicle%20software%20for%20the%20BMW%20Group%20means%20working%20with%20top-class%20processes%20and%20tools%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20gives%20Indian%2