26quot%3Bunlikely%26quot%3B%20he%20would%20contribute%20to%20any%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20chose%20to%20back%20a%20candidate%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20provide%20a%20very%20detailed%20explanation%20of%20why%20I%20am%20endorsing%20one%20or%20the%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20close%20Musk%20watchers%2C%20however%2C%20this%20seemed%20to%20edge%20away%20from%20a%20firm%20pledge%20days%20earlier%20to%20stay%20above%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20as%20Trump%20is%20picking%20up%20the%20phone%20to%20call%20multi-billionaires%2C%20hoping%20they%20will%20open%20their%20checkbooks%20and%20come%20to%20his%20rescue%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECold-calling%20those%20richer%20than%20him%20is%20not%20something%20Trump%20enjoys%2C%20but%20the%20former%20president%20is%20trailing%20Biden%20badly%20in%20fundraising%20and%20the%20campaign%20has%20still%20eight%20months%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBillionaire%20breakfast%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20public%2C%20and%20controversial%2C%20figures%2C%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20have%20not%20always%20seen%20eye%20to%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20for%20one%2C%20is%20not%20a%20believer%20in%20electric%20cars%20such%20as%20those%20that%20Musk%2C%20who%20is%20also%20chief%20at%20Tesla%2C%20has%20championed%20--%20he%20has%20ridiculed%20them%20for%20being%20inconvenient%20and%20dependent%20on%20government%20subsidies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%202016-2020%20presidency%2C%20Musk%20kept%20his%20distance%20--%20though%20that%20was%20before%20his%20public%20tilt%20to%20the%20far%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20flirted%20with%20Trump%20alternatives%20in%20the%20Republican%20primary%2C%20expressing%20support%20for%20Florida%20governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20and%20entrepeneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20before%20they%20flamed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservers%20agree%20that%20Trump%20has%20remained%20quiet%20on%20Musk's%20trans