22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20team.%20The%20change%2C%20which%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20most%20talked%20about%20topics%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%2C%20hasn't%20just%20had%20fans%20but%20also%20some%20former%20cricketers%20baffled.%20Navjot%20Singh%20Sidhu%2C%20former%20India%20cricketer-turned-commentator%2C%20echoed%20the%20sentiments%20of%20thousands%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20fans%20as%20he%20asked%20what%20wrong%20did%20the%20Hitman%20do%2C%20to%20be%20removed%20as%20Mumbai's%20skipper.%20While%20Rohit%20continues%20to%20lead%20the%20Indian%20national%20cricket%20team%2C%20it's%20Hardik%20who%20captains%20his%20IPL%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20can%20digest%20the%20fact%20that%20India's%20hero%2C%20India's%20captain%2C%20is%20not%20the%20captain%20of%20our%20franchise.%20'What%20wrong%20has%20he%20done%3F'%20is%20what%20fans%20of%20the%20franchise%20would%20be%20thinking%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Navjot%20Sidhu%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41747-navjot-singh-bhagwantsingh-sidhu-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENavjot%20Sidhu%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20does%20he%20have%20to%20do%3F%20There%20is%20nothing%20that%20succeeds%20like%20success.%20If%20he%20had%20won%20these%20two%20matches%2C%20there%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20any%20noise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20rumours%20that%20Hardik%20would%20be%20elevated%20as%20India's%20skipper%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20shortest%20format%2C%20and%20would%20lead%20the%20team%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20But%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20confirmed%20that%20Rohit%20would%20remain%20India's%20skipper%20and%20captain