%20behind%20have%20now%20been%20struggling%20for%20days%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20their%20ship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20have%20never%20had%20an%20experience%20like%20this%20before%2C''%20said%20one%20of%20the%20abandoned%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20passengers%20were%20late%20getting%20back%20to%20the%20ship%20on%20March%2027%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Norwegian%20Cruise%20Line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Eight%20guests%20who%20were%20on%20the%20island%20on%20their%20own%20or%20with%20a%20private%20tour%20missed%20the%20last%20tender%20back%20to%20the%20vessel%2C%20therefore%20not%20meeting%20the%20all-aboard%20time%20of%C2%A03%20p.m.%C2%A0local%20time%2C''%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''While%20this%20is%20a%20very%20unfortunate%20situation%2C%20guests%20are%20responsible%20for%20ensuring%20they%20return%20to%20the%20ship%20at%20the%20published%20time%2C%20which%20is%20communicated%20broadly%20over%20the%20ship's%20intercom%2C%20in%20the%20daily%20communication%20and%20posted%20just%20before%20exiting%20the%20vessel.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stranded%20South%20Carolina%20couple%20Jill%20and%20Jay%20Campbell%20said%C2%A0there%20was%20an%20issue%20with%20their%20tour%20on%20the%20island%2C%20and%20the%20guide%20failed%20to%20return%20them%20to%20the%20ship%20on%20time%20on%20Friday.%20However%2C%20when%20they%20arrived%20at%20the%20port%2C%20the%20ship%20was%20still%20anchored%2C%20and%20the%20island's%20Coast%20Guard%20assisted%20them%20in%20getting%20back%20onboard%20via%20a%20boat.%20However%2C%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20ship%20allegedly%20declined%20to%20let%20them%20reenter%20the%20vessel%20and%20they%20were%20left%20there%20without%20their%20possessions%2C%20money%2C%20or%20vital%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwpde.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fcouple-stranded-african-island-norwegian-cruise-line-passengers-abandoned-ship-captain-allegedly-denies-reentry-so-tom-and-prncipe-coast-guard-south-carolina-march-29-2024%5C%22%3ECNN%20affiliate%20WPDE%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20passengers%20spent%2015%20hours%20travelling%20through%20six%20countries%C2%A0to%20try%20to%20rejoin%20their%20ship%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Gambia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Campbells%20also%20said%20that%20several%20members%20of%20the%20group%20are%20elderly%2C%20another%20is%20a%20paraplegic%20and%20one%20woman%20is%20pregnant.%20They%20said%20one%20member%20of%20the%20group%20had%20been%20without%20his%20heart%20medication%20for%20five%20days%20and%20had%20become%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20passengers%20are%20now%20heading%20to%20a%20port%20in%20Senegal%2C%20where%20the%20cruise%20is%20set%20to%20dock%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20looked%20at%20some%20type%20of%20van%20transportation%20for%20eight%20people%2C%20the%20quadriplegic%20woman%20included%2C%20driving%20from%20here.%20We%20have%20to%20cross%20the%20ferry%20to%20get%20into%20Senegal%2C''%20Jay%20Campbell%20told%20%3Cem%3EWPDE.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20just%20learned%20from%20the%20gentleman%20that%20the%20ferry%20hadn't%20been%20working%2C%20but%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98No%20problem%20if%20the%20ferry%20is%20not%20working%2C%20we%20will%20get%20another%20little%20boat%20and%20then%20pick%20up%20a%20car%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20And%20then%20once%20we%20get%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20Senegal%2C%20it's%20another%20four-hour%20drive%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712025240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcog38sog_norwegian-cruise-ship-_625x300_02_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F8-passengers-stranded-on-african-island-after-norwegian-cruise-ship-leaves-them-behind-5355949%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Notably%2C%20the%20passengers%20were%20late%20getting%20back%20to%20the%20ship%20on%20March%2027%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20N