Maritime%20researchers%20located%20the%20remnants%20of%20a%20long-lost%20steamer%20ship%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20western%20Michigan%20using%20sonar%20and%20historical%20newspaper%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flake-superior-shipwrecks-found-solve-1914-wwi-mystery-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichigan%20Shipwreck%20Research%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bremarkably%20intact%26quot%3B%20steamship%20Milwaukee%20during%20an%20event%20last%20month%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMichiganShipwreckResearchAssociation%2Fposts%2Fpfbid026dRyv8Rq7quzmxLV3nNXA95sfz7yazF7qwVUPHddj7ejkAvv8viW6HMQEYEFZKral%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20135-foot-long%20steamship%20had%20been%20lost%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20Lake%20Michigan%20ever%20since%20it%20sank%20in%20about%20360%20feet%20of%20water%20after%20colliding%20with%20another%20ship%20in%20July%201886.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20with%20the%20shipwreck%20association%20first%20spotted%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20Milwaukee%20in%20June%202023%20while%20using%20side-scan%20sonar%2C%20mapping%20technology%20used%20for%20detecting%20and%20imaging%20seafloor%20objects%2C%20the%20organization%20said.%20They%20spent%20the%20next%20few%20months%20working%20to%20film%20the%20wreck%20and%20confirm%20its%20identity%2C%20ultimately%20employing%20a%20remote-operated%20vehicle%2C%20or%20ROV%2C%20built%20specifically%20for%20this%20project%2C%20according%20to%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20organization%20relied%20heavily%20on%20historical%20newspapers%20recounting%20the%20Milwaukee's%20sinking%20to%20corroborate%20the%20wreck's%20identity%2C%20matching%20the%20steamer's%20intended%20course%20with%20its%20exact%20resting%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNews%20accounts%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20study%20of%20water%20currents%2C%20led%20us%20to%20the%20Milwaukee%20after%20only%20two%20days%20searching%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neel%20Zoss%2C%20the%20researcher%20who%20first%20spotted%20the%20wreck%20on%20sonar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Milwaukee%20is%20the%2019th%20shipwreck%20the%20association%20has%20discovered%20off%20the%20shores%20of%20Michigan.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20group%20announced%20the%20discoveries%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-locate-ironton-shipwreck-lake-huron-life-boat-attached-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E190-foot%20cargo%20vessel%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sank%20in%20Lake%20Huron%20amid%20blustery%20winds%20in%201894%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshipwrecks-maritime-history-schooner-trinidad-sinking-wisconsin-lake-michigan-science-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E140-foot%20schooner%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sank%20in%20Lake%20Michigan%20in%201881.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Northern%20Transportation%20Company%20of%20Ohio%20first%20commissioned%20the%20Milwaukee%20in%201868%20as%20a%20passenger%20steamer%2C%20according%20to%20the%20association.%20The%20three-deck%20ship%20spent%2018%20years%20carrying%20settlers%20and%20supplies%20westward%20across%20the%20Great%20Lakes%20before%20it%20sank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Milwaukee%20departed%20Chicago%20on%20July%209%2C%201868%2C%20headed%20for%20Muskegon%20to%20retrieve%20a%20load%20of%20lumber%2C%20according%20to%20newspaper%20accounts%20of%20its%20sinking.%20A%20similar%20ship%2C%20the%20C.%20Hickox%2C%20left%20Muskegon%20that%20same%20night%2C%20headed%20for%20Chicago%20with%20a%20full%20load%20of%20lumber%2C%20the%20association%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaters%20were%20initially%20calm%20when%20a%20lookout%20on%20the%20Milwaukee%20spotted%20lights%20from%20the%20Hickox%20across%20the%20lake.%20But%20a%20thick%20fog%20soon%20blanketed%20the%20lake%2C%20leaving