3E%26quot%3BThat%20became%20a%20wake-up%20call%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20realized%20I%20hadn't%20been%20spending%20enough%20time%20with%20my%20family.%20I%20worked%20very%20long%20hours%20and%20stayed%20in%20the%20camps%20most%20of%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Tan's%20career%20transition%20was%20a%20lot%20harder%20than%20anticipated.%20Tan%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20left%20the%20SAF%20without%20any%20job%20offers%20and%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20his%20savings%20while%20job%20hunting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20wasn't%20just%20about%20money.%20Tan%2C%20who'd%20spent%20his%20entire%20working%20life%20in%20the%20army%2C%20said%20he%20didn't%20know%20what%20kind%20of%20role%20he%20wanted%20or%20his%20dream%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20wasn't%20alone%20in%20facing%20these%20challenges.%20Veterans%20BI%20spoke%20to%20faced%20similar%20challenges%20navigating%20the%20loss%20of%20identity%20when%20they%20left%20service%20or%20struggling%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20corporate%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20contextualizing%20the%20skills%20they'd%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20military%20and%20maintaining%20their%20resilience%2C%20the%20veterans%20told%20BI%2C%20was%20their%20key%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELeaving%20the%20military%20means%20losing%20a%20core%20part%20of%20your%20identity%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you'll%20have%20to%20find%20it%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jiahui%20Ong%2C%2026%2C%20served%20in%20the%20SAF%20for%20five%20years%20before%20leaving%20for%20the%20private%20sector.%20She%20is%20now%20on%20a%20career%20break.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fa94b2895d8220303271a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJiahui%20Ong%2C%2026%2C%20served%20in%20the%20SAF%20for%20five%20years%20before%20leaving%20for%20the%20private%20sector.%20She%20is%20now%20on%20a%20career%20break.%3Cp%3EJi