o%20do%20it%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20got%20older%2C%20I%20found%20some%20of%20my%20father's%20habits%20rubbed%20off%20on%20me.%20When%20video%20stores%20were%20all%20the%20rage%2C%20I'd%20run%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20before%20paying%20a%20late%20fee.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20can%20say%20I've%20never%20paid%20a%20late%20fee%20on%20anything.%20Ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20friends%20in%20college%20were%20loading%20up%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%3Ecredit%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20big%20purchases%2C%20I%20took%20on%20a%20part-time%20job.%20Then%20another.%20I%20always%20ensured%20I%20had%20ample%20spending%20money%20of%20my%20own.%20I%20know%20people%20who%20pay%20only%20the%20minimum%20each%20month%20on%20their%20cards%3B%20that%20never%20made%20fiscal%20sense%20to%20me.%20I%20often%20use%20cash%20to%20help%20me%20better%20balance%20my%20finances%20so%20there%20are%20no%20surprises%20when%20the%20bills%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20to%20travel%2C%20and%2C%20as%20a%20teacher%2C%20I'm%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20summers%20off.%20From%20South%20America%20to%20safaris%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20there%20are%20no%20limits%20on%20destinations.%20Instead%2C%20I%20trade%20fancy%20hotels%20for%20hostels%20or%20host%20families%2C%20or%20even%20cat-sit%20for%20free%20or%20reduced%20lodging.%20I%20scour%20the%20internet%20for%20hours%2C%20sometimes%20days%2C%20until%20I%20find%20the%20best%20fare.%20I've%20never%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20missing%20out%2C%20and%20it%20allows%20me%20to%20get%20to%20know%20the%20locals%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20only%20people%20without%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%20on%20my%20phone.%20I%20will%20walk%20for%20hours%20or%20take%20public%20transportation%20before%20taking%20a%20car%20service.%20All%20these%20little%20things%20add%20up%2C%20and%20I%20have%20never%20found%20myself%20in%20debt.%C