%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20sweetness%20of%20doing%20nothing%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20a%20secluded%20region%20in%20Panchgani%2C%20a%20common%20question%20that%20Alka%20and%20Prachi%20are%20often%20asked%20is%20%E2%80%98Are%20there%20any%20activities%20to%20do%20near%20the%20villa%3F%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9CI%20tell%20my%20guests%20that%20there%20are%20no%20activities.%20Many%20of%20them%20are%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20this%20response%2C%20but%20I%20do%20this%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20make%20them%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20doing%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Alka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20property%20offers%20numerous%20engaging%20activities%2C%20such%20as%20gardening%2C%20pottery%2C%20star%20gazing%2C%20and%20bonfires%2C%20the%20duo%20encourages%20their%20guests%20to%20do%20nothing%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20sweetness%20in%20doing%20nothing%2C%20which%20most%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20about.%20We%20encourage%20our%20guests%20to%20sit%20on%20the%20balcony%20or%20in%20common%20areas%2C%20sip%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%2C%20and%20just%20enjoy%20the%20view.%20Listen%20to%20the%20music%20of%20nature%20and%20indulge%20in%20the%20food%20made%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20this%2C%20Avabodha%20also%20hosts%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288478%2Fiit-guwahati-prosthetic-leg-suitable-for-deep-squatting-yoga-price%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20yoga%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20artist%20retreats%20where%20artists%20are%20welcome%20to%20do%20soul-searching%20at%20the%20property.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20an%20artist%20myself%2C%20and%20the%20villa%20is%20full%20of%20paintings%20given%20to%20us%20by%20our%20guests%20from%20the%20artist%20retreats.%20Before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20Wi-Fi%20at%20the%20property.%20We%20left%20a%20note%20for%20our%20guests%20to%20talk%20to%2